00:07:20.300 --> 00:07:22.220
In conclusion, here
are some things

00:07:22.220 --> 00:07:26.000
to think about when
using closed testing.

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:28.820
Create a strong and
diverse tester community.

00:07:28.820 --> 00:07:32.360
Remember, these players
will be critical in shaping

00:07:32.360 --> 00:07:35.180
the initial direction
of your game.

00:07:35.180 --> 00:07:38.330
Experiment with new gameplay
mechanics and content.

00:07:38.330 --> 00:07:40.574
