00:13:52.750 --> 00:13:55.300
Remember to continuously
evaluate your processes

00:13:55.300 --> 00:13:58.150
around development and testing.

00:13:58.150 --> 00:14:00.980
See what works,
what doesn't work.

00:14:00.980 --> 00:14:04.690
