review individually

00:16:26.900 --> 00:16:30.770
thousands of devices,
identify relevant criteria,

00:16:30.770 --> 00:16:33.780
such as RAM, SOC, or CPU.

00:16:33.780 --> 00:16:36.520
Since last year, we've
added new filtering methods,

00:16:36.520 --> 00:16:40.520
so for example, the screen size,
density, and application binary

00:16:40.520 --> 00:16:41.750
interface.

00:16:41.750 --> 00:16:45.380
As well, since last year, we
